hopobject.body: Could you ask her to call me? was ist tadalista “Mr. Chairman, it would be preferable not to, not because there is any intention or any plan or any desire whatsoever to have boots on the ground … But in the event Syria imploded, for instance, or in the event there was a threat of a chemical weapons cache falling into the hands of al-Nusra or someone else … I don't want to take off the table an option that might or might not be available to a president of the United States to secure our country.”
